# 1️⃣ Why did you use **transfer learning** instead of training from scratch?

**Answer**

Training a deep CNN from scratch requires **a very large dataset and high computational cost**. Transfer learning allows us to use **pre-trained models that already learned general visual features**, which improves performance and reduces training time.

