# 2️⃣ What is the difference between **fine-tuning and transfer learning**?

**Answer**

In **transfer learning**, we use a pre-trained model and only train the final layers.
In **fine-tuning**, we unfreeze some deeper layers and train them to adapt the model better to the new dataset.

